\begin{center}
{\bf\LARGE 87neV parxkaraNa.}\\
\vskip .3cm
{\bf Adi, ACaCx, sarayxdhana I $3$riMda utatxravanunx tegiya takakxdu.}\\
\vskip .3cm
{\bf\large sUtarx.} 
